# Compiled artifacts from vendored sources — regenerated via `make vendor-*`.
# Source submodules under vendor/ ARE tracked; only the root /lib/ is ignored
# (anchored so it can't also swallow nested dirs like .githooks/lib/).
/lib/
.wip/

# Claude Code session-local data: memory db, settings.local.json,
# scheduled tasks, worktrees, workgroup coordination state.
.claude/

# OAuth client credentials — bundle resource read at runtime by
# OAuthClientConfig. The .example.json template IS tracked; the live
# file with real keys is not. Per RFC 8252 / PKCE the values are
# semi-public, but we keep them out of the repo so a fork/clone
# doesn't inherit our app registrations.
DiskJockeyApplication/Resources/OAuthClients.json
